chunk_title: Azure Role-based access controls (Azure RBAC) for adding data sources
chunk_content: Azure Role-based access controls (Azure RBAC) for adding data sourcesTo use Azure OpenAI On Your Data fully, you need to set one or more Azure RBAC roles. See Use Azure OpenAI On Your Data securely for more information.
